name: MAP
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Finding the way.

Be aware that the map is just an indicator, the territory could have changed. A map/pattern that you are running might be outdated.

Find the way

Take action to create your own map. Your own path through life. Be guided from within, learn what is you and what is not you. Be guided by the blueprint of who you are not old outdated patterns that may not serve you any longer. The territory has probably changed so old maps wont work, they’ll make it 
difficult. Be present to where you are and find your own way. Know and learn the pattern of who you are at your core, that is all the map you need in this world.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
